%% SC-03 · 错题详情查看与标签管理 · owner=[s7, s3] · mockup=P07
flowchart TD
  Start([从 P06 列表点 item]) --> Fetch[GET /wrongbook/items/:id]
  Fetch --> FetchOK{200?}
  FetchOK -->|是| Render[渲染题干+图片+AI+标签+历史]
  FetchOK -->|404| Gone[显示"已被删除"]
  Render --> Action{用户操作}
  Action -->|编辑标签| EditTag[Sheet 弹出 · 勾选标签]
  Action -->|删除| ConfirmDel[确认对话]
  Action -->|分享| Share[生成 share_token · 跳 P17]
  Action -->|返回| Back[→ P06]
  EditTag --> PutTag[PUT /wrongbook/items/:id/tags]
  PutTag --> Render
  ConfirmDel -->|确认| Del[DELETE /wrongbook/items/:id · 软删]
  ConfirmDel -->|取消| Render
  Del --> Back
